    "title": "关于修订大闸蟹商品管理、赔付管理及兑换无忧服务规则的公示",
    "followRuleId": "1285221664216453120",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 20pt; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">您好，为适应业务发展，将修订</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=871314268123959296\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">《京东开放平台大闸蟹商品管理规则》</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1189043937948602368\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">《京东开放平台生鲜大闸蟹赔付管理规范》</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">和</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=587324745217871872\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">《京东开放平台兑换无忧服务规则》</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">，公示期：2025年9月17日- 2025年9月23日，于2025年9月24日正式生效，<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: left; text-indent: 26.6667px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span> </span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"width: 100.0%; border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 19.85pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 15.32%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"15%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">规则名称</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.5%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">调整点</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.08%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">调整前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.1%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">调整后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 15.32%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" rowspan=\"10\" width=\"15%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东开放平台大闸蟹商品管理规则</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.5%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #171717; background: white;\">2.1.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #171717; background: white;\">关于商品命名</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.08%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">如标注区间值，则区间浮动范围必须&le;0.3两</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.1%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">如标注区间值，则区间浮动范围必须&le;0.3两（礼券商品不得标注区间值）</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 26.5%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #171717; background: white;\">2.1.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #171717; background: white;\">品质服务保障</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.08%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">礼券：兑换无忧、30天价保、足斤足两（一赔二）、保鲜活</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">活蟹：足斤足两（一赔二）、保鲜活、全程冷链、专线专配</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.1%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">礼券：兑换无忧、30天价保、足斤足两、保鲜活</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">活蟹：足斤足两、保鲜活、全程冷链、专线专配</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 26.5%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2.2.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">礼券版面信息要求</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.08%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">发售方：***公司</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.1%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">委托方：***公司</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 29.08%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">序列号申请需以&ldquo;英文字母+SKU序列号+数字&ldquo;的组合形式，字母建议为品牌中文拼音的首字母缩写的前5位，如果不超过5位，则选择全部拼音首字母即可。例，品牌名称&ldquo;京东生鲜&ldquo;，那么卡号前缀统一为&rdquo;JDSX&ldquo;; SKU序列号为01-99固定数字，不同的SKU，SKU序列号需不同，便于分辨同一商家不同SKU的卡券，防止仓库混扫描。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">示例如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">合规命名：卡号：JDSXX01888888888</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">【英文字母-JXS（全部大写且最多不超过5位）+SKU序列号-01（01-99）+数字-888888888（最多为9位）】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">违规命名：卡号：JXS888888888或2268800001。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.1%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">序列号申请需以&ldquo;英文字母+SKU序列号+数字&ldquo;的组合形式，总位数13位（前5位为前缀，后8位为后缀），字母需为供应商简码的前3位字母，如果不超过3位，则选择全部简码即可。例：供应商简码为ABC，那么卡号前缀统一为&ldquo;ABC &ldquo;；SKU序列号为01-99固定数字，不同的SKU，SKU序列号需不同，便于分辨同一商家不同SKU的卡券，防止仓库混扫描。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">示例如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">合规命名：卡号：ABC0188888888、ABC0288888888</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">【英文字母-JXS（全部大写且最多不超过3位）+SKU序列号-01（01-99）+数字-88888888（最多为8位）】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">违规命名：卡号：JXS888888888或2268800001。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 26.5%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">预售和预订/预定要求</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.08%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.1%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">京东渠道销售的活蟹及礼券商品提前销售行为需符合类目要求规定，礼券商品不允许参与任何预售/预订/预定等提前销售性质的活动，活蟹商品不允许参与任何预售活动，仅允许设置不超过7天的预订/预定时效。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 26.5%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">3.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">抽检方式</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.08%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">感官抽检频次依据各品牌周销售数量划分</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.1%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"29%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">感官抽检频次依据各SKU周销售数量划分</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 26.5%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-fa